			<segment state="initial">
				<source>Can I contribute to WKND?</source>
				<target>¿Puedo contribuir a WKND?</target>
			</segment>
		</unit>
		<unit id="11" matecat:resname="data-node-path=/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_2/text" matecat:restype="x-attribute_name_value" matecat:x-is-multi-value="false" matecat:x-node-path="/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_2/text" matecat:x-property-name="text" matecat:x-restype="x-jcr-html" name="/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_2/text/text" matecat:segment-id="42859707">
			<mda:metadata>
				<mda:metaGroup id="word_count_tu.11.0" category="row_xml_attribute">
					<mda:meta type="x-matecat-raw">41</mda:meta>
					<mda:meta type="x-matecat-weighted">34.85</mda:meta>
				</mda:metaGroup>
			</mda:metadata>
			<segment state="initial">
				<source>&lt;p&gt;Yes!&amp;nbsp; If you have the expertise and&amp;nbsp;experiences&amp;nbsp;to share, we’ll provide the platform to spread it.&amp;nbsp; As a Guest Writer, you will play an integral role in helping people find fun and cool things to do in your community.&lt;/p&gt;
</source>
				<target>¡&lt;p&gt;Sí! &amp;nbsp; Si tienes la experiencia y las experiencias para compartir, te proporcionaremos la plataforma para difundirlas. &amp;nbsp; Como escritor invitado, desempeñarás un papel integral para ayudar a las personas a encontrar cosas divertidas y geniales que hacer en tu comunidad.&#10;&lt;/p&gt;</target>
			</segment>
		</unit>
		<unit id="12" matecat:resname="data-node-path=/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1571070705187" matecat:restype="x-attribute_name_value" matecat:x-is-multi-value="false" matecat:x-node-path="/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1571070705187" matecat:x-property-name="cq:panelTitle" matecat:x-restype="x-jcr-property" name="/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1571070705187/cq:panelTitle" matecat:segment-id="42859708">
