				</mda:metaGroup>
			</mda:metadata>
			<segment state="initial">
				<source>How often is WKDN updated?</source>
				<target>¿Con qué frecuencia se actualiza WKDN?</target>
			</segment>
		</unit>
		<unit id="13" matecat:resname="data-node-path=/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1571070705187/text" matecat:restype="x-attribute_name_value" matecat:x-is-multi-value="false" matecat:x-node-path="/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1571070705187/text" matecat:x-property-name="text" matecat:x-restype="x-jcr-html" name="/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1571070705187/text/text" matecat:segment-id="42859709">
			<mda:metadata>
				<mda:metaGroup id="word_count_tu.13.0" category="row_xml_attribute">
					<mda:meta type="x-matecat-raw">43</mda:meta>
					<mda:meta type="x-matecat-weighted">36.54</mda:meta>
				</mda:metaGroup>
			</mda:metadata>
			<segment state="initial">
				<source>&lt;p&gt;WKND is updated daily to provide you with the latest in-depth articles on fun activities that we’ve recently exploring and new adventures that are available for you to discover.&amp;nbsp; Come back often to see the latest or subscribe to our social feeds.&lt;/p&gt;
</source>
				<target>&lt;p&gt;WKND se actualiza diariamente para proporcionarte los últimos artículos detallados sobre actividades divertidas que hemos explorado recientemente y nuevas aventuras que están disponibles para que descubras. &amp;nbsp; Vuelve a menudo para ver las últimas noticias o suscríbete a nuestras redes sociales.&#10;&lt;/p&gt;</target>
			</segment>
		</unit>
		<unit id="14" matecat:resname="data-node-path=/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1571070718887" matecat:restype="x-attribute_name_value" matecat:x-is-multi-value="false" matecat:x-node-path="/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1571070718887" matecat:x-property-name="cq:panelTitle" matecat:x-restype="x-jcr-property" name="/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1571070718887/cq:panelTitle" matecat:segment-id="42859710">
			<mda:metadata>
				<mda:metaGroup id="word_count_tu.14.0" category="row_xml_attribute">
					<mda:meta type="x-matecat-raw">4</mda:meta>
					<mda:meta type="x-matecat-weighted">3.4</mda:meta>
				</mda:metaGroup>
			</mda:metadata>
			<segment state="initial">
				<source>When was WKND founded?</source>
				<target>¿Cuándo se fundó WKND?</target>
			</segment>
		</unit>
		<unit id="15" matecat:resname="data-node-path=/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1571070718887/text" matecat:restype="x-attribute_name_value" matecat:x-is-multi-value="false" matecat:x-node-path="/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1571070718887/text" matecat:x-property-name="text" matecat:x-restype="x-jcr-html" name="/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1571070718887/text/text" matecat:segment-id="42859711">
			<mda:metadata>
				<mda:metaGroup id="word_count_tu.15.0" category="row_xml_attribute">
					<mda:meta type="x-matecat-raw">80</mda:meta>
					<mda:meta type="x-matecat-weighted">68</mda:meta>
				</mda:metaGroup>
			</mda:metadata>
			<segment state="initial">
				<source>&lt;p&gt;WKND was created in 2015 when our founders, Daniel and Kilian, realized that their friends and family were constantly using them as resources to find fun things to do while they were in Los Angeles. They loved sharing ideas about fun events and activities they knew of, but wanted to be able to do it at larger scale across communities.&amp;nbsp; They decided to start WKND as a way to share their insights and experiences with as many people as possible.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
</source>
				<target>&lt;p&gt;WKND se creó en 2015 cuando nuestros fundadores, Daniel y Kilian, se dieron cuenta de que sus amigos y familiares los usaban constantemente como recursos para encontrar cosas divertidas que hacer mientras estaban en Los Ángeles. Les encantaba compartir ideas sobre eventos y actividades divertidas que conocían, pero querían poder hacerlo a mayor escala en todas las comunidades.&amp;nbsp; Decidieron comenzar WKND como una forma de compartir sus ideas y experiencias con tantas personas como fuera posible.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&#10;&lt;/p&gt;</target>
			</segment>
		</unit>
		<unit id="16" matecat:resname="data-node-path=/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1572027287775" matecat:restype="x-attribute_name_value" matecat:x-is-multi-value="false" matecat:x-node-path="/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1572027287775" matecat:x-property-name="cq:panelTitle" matecat:x-restype="x-jcr-property" name="/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1572027287775/cq:panelTitle" matecat:segment-id="42859712">
			<mda:metadata>
				<mda:metaGroup id="word_count_tu.16.0" category="row_xml_attribute">
					<mda:meta type="x-matecat-raw">6</mda:meta>
					<mda:meta type="x-matecat-weighted">5.09</mda:meta>
				</mda:metaGroup>
			</mda:metadata>
			<segment state="initial">
				<source>Is a hot dog a sandwich?</source>
				<target>¿Un perrito caliente es un sándwich?</target>
			</segment>
		</unit>
		<unit id="17" matecat:resname="data-node-path=/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1572027287775/text" matecat:restype="x-attribute_name_value" matecat:x-is-multi-value="false" matecat:x-node-path="/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1572027287775/text" matecat:x-property-name="text" matecat:x-restype="x-jcr-html" name="/content/wknd/language-masters/es-es/faqs/jcr:content/root/container/container/accordion/item_1572027287775/text/text" matecat:segment-id="42859713">
			<mda:metadata>
				<mda:metaGroup id="word_count_tu.17.0" category="row_xml_attribute">
					<mda:meta type="x-matecat-raw">42</mda:meta>
					<mda:meta type="x-matecat-weighted">35.7</mda:meta>
				</mda:metaGroup>
			</mda:metadata>
			<segment state="initial">
				<source>&lt;p&gt;While it may be described as meat between two pieces of bread, a hot dog is just a sandwich in the same way Michael Jordan was just a basketball player or William Shakespeare was just a playwright.&amp;nbsp; Technically true, but vastly understated.&lt;/p&gt;
</source>
				<target>&lt;p&gt;Si bien puede describirse como carne entre dos trozos de pan, un perrito caliente es solo un sándwich de la misma manera que Michael Jordan era solo un jugador de baloncesto o William Shakespeare era solo un dramaturgo.&amp;nbsp; Técnicamente cierto, pero muy subestimado.&#10;&lt;/p&gt;</target>
			</segment>
